Package: com.sinfool.statusbardoubleheightisusingbarcolorcustomier
Name: Status Bar - Double Height "Is Using" Bar Color Customizer
Author: Sinfool
Description: Allows you to set a custom background & text color for all double height "Is Using..." status bars (i.e. the red, green & blue bars when in a call, recording audio, navigating or tethering etc.). Allows you to set a custom background & text color for all double height "Is Using..." status bars (i.e. the red, green & blue bars when in a call, recording audio, navigating or tethering etc.).
 .
 By default, I set the background to a dark semi transparent color and the text to white but you can change the colors to your liking.
 .
 [v.1] Tested on an iPad mini2 11.1.2.  (4-30-18)
